messages.title: YOU CAN'T TRUST BORIS JOHNSON'S TORIES
messages.content: Boris Johnson's sham Brexit deal will damage our economy, our public services and the fabric of the United Kingdom. It is a charter for deregulation and a race to the bottom. And it will put Scotland and Northern Ireland on a path that will lead away from the UK.

messages.title: Labour Will
messages.content: Get Brexit sorted in six months. Labour will put control of Brexit back in the hands of the people in a new referendum with a real choice between a sensible leave deal or remain.
